This milestone was about knowing what your machine can run — and keeping your
chats organized. The **hardware-fit estimator** and **GGUF quant metadata**
enrichment tell you whether a model fits before you download it, and a
**GPU-layer toggle** gives you control over offloading. Conversations gained
an **archive** UI, **rename / delete**, and **system-prompt persistence**,
with a proper generation-error state.

